前 Black Midi 成员 Geordie Greep 分享了不拘一格的新单曲“Blues” https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-owned-of-black-midi-shares-electic-new-single-blues-3798648?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=geordie-greep-owned- of-black-midi-shares-不拘一格-新-单曲-布鲁斯Anagricel DuranTue, 01 Oct 2024 14:07:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3798648 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔迪·格里普。图片来源：Yis Kid" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是这位音乐家即将发行的专辑“The New Sound”中发行的第二首歌曲</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-formerly-of-black-midi-shares-eclectic-new-single-blues-3798648">Geordie Greep（前 Black Midi 成员）分享了不拘一格的新单曲“Blues”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔迪·格里普。图片来源：Yis Kid" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Geordie-Greep.-Credit-Yis-Kid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Geordie-Greep">乔迪·格里普 (Geordie Greep)</a>分享了他即将发行的首张个人专辑《The New Sound》中不拘一格的新单曲《Blues》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-interview-black-midi-split-solo-album-new-sound-3790258">乔迪·格里普 (Geordie Greep) 谈论“新声音”和 Black Midi 的分歧：“我会用不同的方式来做”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌以一个错误的开头开始，看到格里普演奏了快速而激烈的吉他即兴演奏，然后是各种乐器的疯狂混合，带有拉丁萨尔萨风格，他唱道： <em>“你是厕所的掠夺者和坟墓的掠夺者/你不必须工作，因为工作是傻瓜的事。”</em></p><p>这位前<a href="/artists/Black-Midi">Black Midi</a>主唱在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/geordie-greep-blues-interview-black-midi-1235113175/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>采访时谈到这首歌时分享道：“我想做一首这样的歌曲，‘哦，看看这个混蛋——话又说回来，我们都是混蛋。我们都已经18岁了。我想做一首关于当你认为自己很糟糕的时候的歌，当你走在街上时你会有这种感觉，你可以想象这是一部电影。就像，多么混蛋啊！这只是一堆有趣的台词串在一起，真的，主题就像 18 岁的自命不凡。” </p><p><iframe title="Geordie Greep - Blues（TV Eye 现场直播）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gNGlbB4Gbyo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首单曲是格里普即将推出的个人专辑中的第二首歌曲。它是继之前发行的主打单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-midi-split-geordie-greep-announces-debut-solo-album-the-new-sound-with-single-holy-holy-3785237">Holy Holy</a> ”之后的。他的LP“The New Sound”将于本周五（10 月 4 日）发行，<a href="https://geordiegreep.ffm.to/newsound" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处预订/预保存</a>。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到专辑的创作时，格里普分享道：“录制《The New Sound》时，这是我第一次没有人可以回答。伴随着我的每一次冲动，我都能完全遵循它的结论。在乐队（Black Midi）中，我们经常有这种‘我们可以做一切’的感觉，但你在这种方法上也受到限制，有时做点别的事情，放手一些事情是件好事。”</p><p>跨越圣保罗和伦敦两大洲的三十多名音乐家参与了这张专辑的制作。 “有些曲目我们已经在其他地方录制过，但它就是不正确，所以我们和新人一起重新录制了它们，”格里普解释道。</p><p> “一半的曲目是在巴西完成的，当地音乐家在最后一刻聚集在一起，”他继续说道。 “他们以前从未听说过我做过的任何事情，他们只是对我制作的演示感兴趣。跟踪工作在一两天内完成。然后我们稍后在伦敦进行了配音。” </p><figure id="attachment_3798665" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798665" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798665" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="乔迪·格里普“The New Sound”专辑封面。信用出版社" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerodie-Greep-The-New-Sound-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3798665" class="wp-caption-text">乔迪·格里普“The New Sound”专辑封面。信用出版社</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>Geordie Greep &#39;The New Sound&#39; 曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.《蓝调》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“泰拉”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“圣哉，圣哉”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“新声音”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“走起来”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“经历一场战争”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“邦戈季节”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“摩托车”</strong><br /> <strong>9.《仿佛华尔兹》</strong><br /> <strong>10.《魔术师》</strong><br /> <strong>11.《如果你只是一场梦》</strong></p><p>几天前，格里普和他的前乐队成员卡梅隆·皮克顿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-midi-are-indefinitely-over-confirms-bassist-and-frontman-3782676">在社交媒体上确认了 Black Midi 乐队的“无限期”结束</a>。</p><p>在 Instagram 直播中，Greep 在回答粉丝询问乐队何时发行新专辑时，在聊天中输入“no more black midi”和“it&#39;s over”。</p><p>他继续说道：“Black Midi 是一支有趣的乐队，但现在已经无限期结束了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geordie-greep-interview-black-midi-split-solo-album-new-sound-3790258">在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，这位歌手透露说，这是“我第一次对我喜欢听的音乐类型非常透明”​到。”</p><p> “我喜欢在 Black Midi 中，但这些歌曲适合与不同的人一起演奏，”他告诉<em>NME</em> 。 “此外，我想开始以我自己的名义做一些更有意义的事情，并尝试一些更通用的事情。​我​知道​我​最终​想要​这么做。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_lpSYkM85r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.