瘦”（原声）</strong><br /> <strong>“电视”（声学）</strong><br /> <strong>“埋葬一个朋友”</strong><br /> <strong>“催产素”（扩展版）</strong><br /> <strong>“你应该看到我戴着王冠”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Guess remix&#39;（Charli XCX 歌曲）</strong><br /> <strong>“我想要的一切”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;BLUE&#39; (现场首演)</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;迷人的&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“我不再想成为你了”</strong><br /> <strong>“海洋之眼”</strong><br /> <strong>《生活之爱》</strong><br /> <strong>“我生来是为了什么？”</strong><br /> <strong>“比以往任何时候都快乐”</strong><br /> <strong>“物以类聚”</strong></p><p>为了准备巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-partners-with-google-maps-to-offer-fans-sustainable-transport-to-upcoming-north-american-tour-3796831">这位歌手与谷歌地图合作</a>，帮助粉丝在前往她的演出时找到可持续的交通和食物选择。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比莉·艾利什 |第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mVvt33l7BwM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>艾利什<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-levitate-in-new-video-for-birds-of-a-feather-3797975">最近分享了“Birds Of A Feather”的音乐视频</a>。这段受超自然启发的视频由艾丹·扎米里 (Aidan Zamiri) 执导，视频中，艾利什 (Eilish) 被无形的力量抓住，将她拖过地板，爬上墙壁。</p><p>其他新闻方面，她将与主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-keaton">迈克尔·基顿</a>一起担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snl-to-kick-off-50th-season-with-coldplay-stevie-nicks-chappell-roan-and-more-3795032">10 月 19 日<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目的音乐嘉宾</a>，她最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-endorse-kamala-harris-for-president-vote-like-your-life-depends-on-it-because-it-does-3794597">支持卡玛拉·哈里斯参加美国总统竞选</a>。</p><p>本周还有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-is-learning-to-do-home-production-without-finneas-3797325">艾利什现在正在学习“在没有她哥哥芬尼斯的情况下进行家庭制作”</a> ，迄今为止，她的三张专辑都是由芬尼斯制作的。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-e